	<h1 class="title">《火星救援》、《X 战警》，这些大片背后都有博纳的投资</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/102277/small/102277.jpg?1432868256" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">韩方航 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-11-06 12:12:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/17186/medium/17186.jpg?1446779427" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


